invalid type: string "\n### Use Case Name:\nTake Quiz\n\n### Use Case ID:\n13\n\n### Description:\nLearner takes a quiz. Upon completion, the received score is displayed, and\nthe learner can see answers or solutions as de\0ned by the instructor.\n\n### Field:\nDescription\n\n### Actor:\nLearner\n\n### Pre-Condition:\n1. Learner must be registered in the course.\n2. The quiz is open for taking.\n’